OL,3,CGaps in Wales asthma care 'led to
OL,4,C1,000 children being admitted to
OL,5,Chospital'
OL,7,FGaps in care has led to more than
OL,8,F1,000 children being admitted to
OL,9,Fhospital in Wales, a charity has said.
OL,11,FAsthma + Lung UK Cymru is calling for
OL,12,Fan urgent review of children's asthma
OL,13,Fcare, warning that unmet targets are
OL,14,Ffuelling a three-year rise in hospital
OL,15,Fadmissions.
OL,17,FNHS Wales admissions data reveals that
OL,18,Fmore than 1,000 children with asthma
OL,19,Fin Wales required emergency care last
OL,20,Fyear. This has risen for three
OL,21,Fconsecutive years.
