OL,7,FData also shows children under-18 from
OL,8,Fthe most deprived areas in Wales
OL,9,Fexperienced almost three times as many
OL,10,Fasthma hospital admissions compared to
OL,11,Fthose from the least deprived areas.
OL,13,FKatie Kwiecinski, a nurse from
OL,14,FYstradgynlais, has a five-year-old son
OL,15,Fwith asthma and says there's a lack of
OL,16,Fawareness around the condition.
OL,18,FShe said: "When Theo first had issues
OL,19,Fwith his breathing, it was a
OL,20,Fterrifying time for us as a family.
