OL,5,Chospital'
OL,7,F"His asthma attacks would often come
OL,8,Fout of the blue, especially at night,
OL,9,Fand we had to call 999 multiple times.
OL,10,FTrying to give a small child an
OL,11,Finhaler through a spacer when they're
OL,12,Falready struggling to breathe was
OL,13,Fincredibly distressing.
OL,15,F"The asthma nurses at Morriston
OL,16,FHospital were fantastic. They gave us
OL,17,Fa care plan that helped us and Theo's
OL,18,Fnursery feel more confident in
OL,19,Fmanaging his condition."
