OL,5,Chospital'
OL,7,FDespite Theo's multiple hospital
OL,8,Fadmissions, Katie said she'd never
OL,9,Freceived any information leaflets or
OL,10,Fguidance beyond that initial care plan.
OL,12,FShe says more resources, education,
OL,13,Fand public awareness are needed so
OL,14,Fthat parents, schools, and communities
OL,15,Fknow how to act in an emergency.
OL,17,F"Theo is now five and much more aware
OL,18,Fof his symptoms. He's learned to
OL,19,Fmanage his asthma daily, and we are so
OL,20,Fproud of him.
