OL,7,F"But the cold winter months remains a
OL,8,Fworrying time, and every cough makes
OL,9,Fus anxious. We do everything we can
OL,10,Fsuch as taking his medicines as
OL,11,Fprescribed, making sure he has his flu
OL,12,Fvaccine, but it's still a stressful
OL,13,Fseason."
