OL,7,FThe data was gathered between 1 August
OL,8,F2021 and 31 July 2023.
OL,10,FJoseph Carter Head of Asthma + Lung UK
OL,11,FCymru says the numbers of children
OL,12,Fending up in hospital shows that
OL,13,Ffamilies are not getting the help they
OL,14,Fneed to manage the condition
OL,15,Feffectively.
