OL,3,CGaps in Wales asthma care 'led to
OL,4,C1,000 children being admitted to
OL,5,Chospital'
OL,7,FHe added: "It has been two years since
OL,8,Fthe findings of the last audit on
OL,9,Fasthma care for children in Wales were
OL,10,Fpublished, yet the critical changes
OL,11,Fneeded to protect children's lung
OL,12,Fhealth have not been made. This lack
OL,13,Fof action is both concerning and
OL,14,Funacceptable.
OL,16,F"We're calling on the Welsh Government
OL,17,Fto urgently review the findings of the
OL,18,Flatest GP audit and implement
OL,19,Fnecessary improvements in children's
OL,20,Fasthma care.
