OL,3,CGaps in Wales asthma care 'led to
OL,4,C1,000 children being admitted to
OL,5,Chospital'
OL,7,F"This is especially critical in
OL,8,Fdeprived areas, where factors such as
OL,9,Fpoor housing, air pollution, and
OL,10,Fhigher smoking rates contribute to
OL,11,Fpoor lung health in children. Without
OL,12,Fstronger action to address complacency
OL,13,Faround asthma, thousands of children
OL,14,Fwill remain at risk. Big changes are
OL,15,Fneeded to protect little lungs."
